data.description: Welcome home! Beautiful well maintained one owner home ready for a new family. This home features granite and stainless in the kitchen hardwood floors in  hall and bedrooms. All interior doors are solid wood. Three bedrooms with a sitting room off the master. Large walk in closet. Large master bath with jetted tub and walk-in shower. A true master suit! In ground pool that comes with a dolphin automatic cleaner. Walking distance to the parade route. Short walk to the beach and a bike ride to down town.
